snippet.title: ZombiU - Tower of London Official Walkthrough [EUROPE]
snippet.description:
Visit the official Website: http://www.zombiu.com
Join us on Facebook: http://www.facebook.com/zombiugame
Only the prepared will survive. Download the mobile app : https://itunes.apple.com/gb/app/zombiu/id574425152?mt=8

Find your way through London's most famous tower... invaded by zombies! Will you make it to the top and reach the helicopter that may be your only chance of getting out alive?
